xvidcore: xvidcore (MPEG-4 compliant video codec)
xvidcore:
xvidcore: The Xvid video codec implements MPEG-4 Simple Profile and Advanced 
xvidcore: Simple Profile standards. It permits compressing and decompressing 
xvidcore: digital video in order to reduce the required bandwidth of video data 
xvidcore: for transmission over computer networks or efficient storage on CDs 
xvidcore: or DVDs. Due to its unrivalled quality Xvid has gained great 
xvidcore: popularity and is used in many other GPLed applications, like e.g. 
xvidcore: Transcode, MEncoder, MPlayer, Xine and many more.
